headline: Truist Raises Genesco Inc. (GCO)’s Price Target by $2
summary: Truist has raised its price target on Genesco Inc. (NYSE:GCO) from $23 to $25, while maintaining a Hold rating on the stock. This comes after Genesco Inc. (NYSE:GCO) reported strong first-quarter results and maintained its full-year profits per share target, despite the company’s current tariff implications.
